                Government Departments (War-Time Records)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1943-03-18/debates/fac8cd7d-6de9-4e4b-aaca-becd0a5d474f/BeveridgeReport(Implementation)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
